heading: United States Capitol Complex (Washington, D.C.).
general-note: Here are entered works treating collectively the U.S. Capitol Building; the Congressional office buildings; the U.S. Botanic Garden; the Capitol grounds; the Jefferson, Madison, and Adams buildings of the Library of Congress; the U.S. Supreme Court Building; the Capitol Power Plant; etc. Works dealing with a specific building or feature are entered under the building or feature, e.g.. Dirksen Senate Office Building (Washington, D.C.)..
